												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/samweller/">Sam Weller</a></h6>
													Sam Weller is the authorized biographer of the bestselling <em>The Bradbury Chronicles: The Life of Ray Bradbury</em> (HarperPerennial, 2006) and <em>Listen to the Echoes: The Ray Bradbury Interviews</em> (Hat and Beard Press, 2017). He has written for the <em>Paris Review</em>, <em>Slate</em>, <em>The Los Angeles Review of Books</em> and many others. Follow him on Bluesky @samwellerauthor.bsky.social or learn more at www.samweller.net																									</div>
